				<td colspan="2"><span><blockquote><b>Quote:</b><br><span class="quote">Does Dreams of Terris have a Mem Blur effect?</span></blockquote>
<br />

<br />
Not to my knowledge. The only place I saw mention of any sort of mem-blur on our mezzes is in the little spell book guide I bought a while ago that lists all spells up to PoP. Its information is...lacking...to be gentle. I would say no.
<br />

<br />
Mezz push will be a thing of the past when you get Lullaby of Morrel. I THOUGHT I would miss it, but nope, never looked back once I got it.</span></td>
