				<td colspan="2"><span>Wiladancer,
<br />

<br />
Only the level 58 Mezz ( <a target="_new" href="http://lucy.allakhazam.com/spell.html?id=1100&amp;source=Live">Dreams of Ayonae</a> ) and the level 60 ( <a target="_new" href="http://lucy.allakhazam.com/spell.html?id=1197&amp;source=Live">Ancient Lullaby of Shadow</a> ) have  memblur components.  None of the 62+ mezz songs do.
<br />

<br />
*waves to fellow Torvonnite*
