				<td colspan="2"><span>Yep, primarily useful for healers and gaters -- the kind of things your personal resists won't stop.  Back when I was 61 or 62, we used to regularly XP on spiders in POD rat caves and I would chain mez them throughout the battle to avoid the heals.  Gate however, is harder to prevent -- it is a much faster casting time and I find mana draining with Ervaj to be a more secure way to stop gating.</span></td>
