				<td colspan="2"><span>I slam first, then I bellow, and if all else fails I will mez.
<br />

<br />
I tend to hunt with pet classes a lot, and although some
<br />
people like the fact that the mob restarts casting right away
<br />
after a mez break, I find that it just locks me in chain mez
<br />
mode and I can't play other songs.  When slam/bellow land
<br />
it gives me a few more seconds on my twist, and sometimes
<br />
it's long enough to secure a dead before next ch/gate mob.
<br />

<br />
I have E-Bellow IV and I use ogre potions to get slam.
<br />

